'''Asuref agraɣlan''' d [[tuddsa]] [[tuddsa tarnabdant|tarnabdant]] yellan di temdint n [[London]], amahil-is yezzi ɣef tlufa ittaken assaɣ ɣer [[izerfan n wemdan]]. Tuddsa ayi teqqar-d d akken tla (tesɛa) ugar n 7 n imelyan n igmamen deg yakk ideggan n umadal.<br/>

Tuddsa n usuref agraɣlan tennulfa-d deg useggas n [[1961]] di London, srid mi i d-yella wefsar n umagrad iddmen azwel n ''imuṭṭifen yettwattun'' deg [[aɣmis|weɣmis]] n [[The Observer]] ass n [[28 mayyu]] [[1961]] <ref name="Forgotten">Benenson, Peter, [https://www.theguardian.com/uk/1961/may/28/fromthearchive.theguardian "The Forgotten Prisoners"], ''The Observer'', 28 May 1961. Retrieved 28 May 2011. {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612135906/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/1961/may/28/fromthearchive.theguardian |date=12 yunyu 2018}}</ref> sɣur umyaru [[Peter Benenson]] i d-irran tamuɣli ɣer truẓi n izerfan n wemdan. Sin akin, deg taggara n umagrad yessuter azrekki (aqader) n ilugan [[asaduf agraɣlan|isudaf igraɣlanen]], akken i yexdem i wakken ad yesmures [[turda tazayezt]] i wakken ad yili uttekki ɣef iduba yettruẓen izerfan n wemdan deg tmura-nsen.

Tuddsa ayi tettarem ad tawi izerfan i d-isegger (i d-yeḍmen) [[Tiṣerriḥt tagraɣlant izerfan n wemdan|ulɣu aseddayan n izerfan n wemdan]], akken i tettarem ad terr tamuɣli n inabaden d teddukliwin tigraɣlanin ɣer waddad n yizerdan n wemdan deg tmura n umadal yakk.

